Antonia Clarke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antonia_Clarke 0 Antonia Clarke (born 24 May 1994) is an English actress and singer best known for her role as Penny Hamilton in the 2014 British horror thriller film Altar. Her other notable films include 2012 epic musical drama film Les Misérables and 2014 American romantic comedy film Magic in the Moonlight.
